              ZURK III: "The City of Glass"                                     In this remarkable story, the adventurer finds himself teleported in the        vicinity of an abandoned palace. After many struggles he discovers a strange    craft which he rode to the stars, landing by a strange domed city               END                                                                             of robots, thinking this to be the city of glass itself. After defeated the     robots, he found his way back to the palace and pulled a lovely princess        out of slumber in snow, and soon saw the city itself:                           END                                                                             It was but a small model, the dream of the people he had revived and saved.     FINISH                                                                          